column5: Well after spending all my income tax money at Bass Pro the other day lol i fly out tomarrow morning. i will be in Winnipeg around 1000am central time, then to Totem Resorts around 1:00-2:00  . ill make sure to stop by every once in a while haha and maybe even post a report or two    with plenty of pictures for that one fine gentleman  .  have a great summer everyone!!  Matt
Have a great one pikeie and remember we like pictures.
enjoy it .. wish I was in your shoes
Have a GREAT summer Matt and let you poor old Dad visit at least once !!!
have a great time....look forward to some 'EPIC' picture filled reports.
Have fun Matt, see you in the fall at you know where...
Ahhhh Youth !!!...  Have a great summer Matthew and enjoy your new job...
You have yourself a great summer Matt Tight lines! Leechman

well it appears Pikeie is too busy 'working' to post . I do know fishing has been awesome ...OFF THE DOCK !!! Walleye , 36" pike and even an OOS Muskie  I know you are having fun Matt , glad to hear you have some pets up there as well  Maybe you can add them to your bug collection !  Looking froward to some pictures.  Dad
If I'm not mistaken, a musky buddy of mine will be up there with his girlfrend working for the summer, his name is Brandon. Good luck and have a fun and safe summer.
